description.narrative:
- Research on the situation and needs of the persons with disabilities carried out;
- Identification of barriers and needs of persons with disabilities in 6 municipalities of the South-East region;
- Developed unified data structure and digitalization of data of members of the National Associations of persons with disabilities;
- Number of trained professionals for provision of work-oriented rehabilitation services;

comment.narrative:
- Currently there is no available data (register) on the number of persons with disabilities and the prevalence of the specific disability regionally;
- There is no system of institutional support for provision of work-oriented rehabilitation to persons with disabilities, or support in their preparation for employment and labour market integration;
- No available data or systematic approach on trained professionals for provision of work-oriented rehabilitation services;

- Situation analysis and identification of the needs of persons with disabilities in three regions (Skopje, Pelagonija and South-East Region);
- Situation analysis and identification of the needs of the persons with disabilities placed in foster families on a national level; 
- Developed unified data structure and digitalization of data of members of the National Associations of persons with disabilities;
- 15 professionals from public institutions and NGOs trained for provision of work-oriented rehabilitation services; 
- 23 persons with disabilities undergo work-oriented rehabilitation process

